roups.form groups the remaining walls for parallel lanes; full constructor syntax, generic specialization, type/generic overload selection, arbitrary source-control-block lowering, source-level restore spelling, general mutable local source lowering, JNI load/call receipts, installed-app native execution, non-adb transport receipts, and fourth-arm mutable-record admission remain named cells rather than being folded into the floor prematurely")))
